'''-{zh-tw:湯瑪斯;zh-tw:湯瑪斯;zh-cn:托马斯}-·-{zh-cn:阿兰;zh-tw:艾倫;zh-hk:阿倫;}-·“湯姆”·威茨'''（{{lang-en|Thomas Alan "Tom" Waits}}，{{bd|1949年|12月7日||}}），美國音樂人、演员。威茨嗓音独特，评论家Daniel Durchholz說他的聲音“像浸入一桶[[波本威士忌|波本威士忌]]，-{zh-hans:熏制;zh-hant:燻製;}-几个月，然后再拿出来”（it was soaked in a vat of bourbon, left hanging in the smokehouse for a few months, and then taken outside and run over with a car.）。<ref>{{cite book | last = Graff | first = Gary | coauthors = Durchholz, Daniel | title = Musichound Rock: The Essential Album Guide | year = 1999 | url = https://archive.org/details/musichoundrockes0000unse_j0b4 | publisher = Omnibus Press | isbn = 0-8256-7256-2 }}</ref>他独特的低音以及对前[[摇滚音樂|摇滚音樂]]元素的吸收构成了他的風格。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://arts.guardian.co.uk/reviews/story/0,11712,1358433,00.html | title=Tom Waits live at the Hammersmith Apollo, London review | accessdate=2001-11-23 | last=Petridis | first=Alexis | publisher=The Guardian newspaper | archive-date=2008-06-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080624230513/http://arts.guardian.co.uk/reviews/story/0,11712,1358433,00.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>威茨還参演了一些電影，包括[[吉姆·贾木许|吉姆·贾木许]]的《[[不法之徒|不法之徒]]》。他为《[[从心出发|从心出发]]》创作的配乐获得了[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]提名。

